<h3 class="font-industry font-extrabold uppercase text-2xl text-center lg:text-left leading-none mb-3"><a href="/military-ranks/">US Military Ranks</a></h3>
<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-2 mt-6">
<div class="mb-5 lg:mb-10">
<a href="/military-ranks/us-army/" class="rank-hov">
<span class="block relative overflow-hidden">
<img src="https://i1.wp.com/cms.sofrep.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/sofrep-us-army-rank-top-hero.jpeg?resize=437,291" class="objec-cover">
<div class="rank-hover r-0"></div>
<div class="rank-name-wrap">
<div class="rank-0 relative">
